    <area target="" research="<img src=&quot;http://musicfamily.org/realm/Factions/picks/ExchangeHighLordSecretTrophy.png&quot; align=&quot;middle&quot;><b> Exchange High Lord</b></p><p>Requirements: 5000 Royal Exchanges<p>Cost: 10 DQig (1e160)<p>Effect: Increase royal exchange bonus by 250%." coords="325,492,382,548" shape="rect">
    <area target="" research="<img src=&quot;http://musicfamily.org/realm/Factions/picks/GenealogistSecretTrophy.png&quot; align=&quot;middle&quot;><b> Genealogist</b></p><p>Requirements: Have a total of 300 Lineage levels across all Lineage.<p>Cost: 1 NoQig (1e180)<p>Effect: Increase the production of all buildings based on the total amount of lineage levels you have.<p>Formula: 2.5 * x^1.25, where x is total amount of lineage levels you have." coords="389,492,446,548" shape="rect">
    <area target="" research="<img src=&quot;http://musicfamily.org/realm/Factions/picks/HolyFrenzySecretTrophy.png&quot; align=&quot;middle&quot;><b> Holy Frenzy</b></p><p><b>Requirement</b>: A2+, In a single reincarnation, have a 3 day combined activity time of Holy Light and Blood Frenzy.<p><b>Effect</b>: While Blood Frenzy or Holy Light are active, increase the production of all buildings.<p><b>Note</b>:Upgrade scales from Holy Light/Blood Frenzy tiers.<p>Formula: (250 * t ^ 2)<p><b>Cost</b>: 100 Dc (1e35)" coords="5,556,62,613" shape="rect">
    <area target="" research="<img src=&quot;http://musicfamily.org/realm/Factions/picks/UniformitySecretTrophy.png&quot; align=&quot;middle&quot;><b> Uniformity</b></p><p><b>Requirement</b>: A2+, With no less than 3 days of playtime, have less than 1 minute of playtime difference for Order, Chaos and Balance alignments.<p><b>Effect</b>: Increases production of all buildings based on time spent as least used alignment.<p><b>Cost</b>: 100 Qid (1e50)<p><b>Formula</b>: 0.7 * min(x ,y, z. s, t ,u) ^ 0.7, where x is neutral time, y is good time, z is evil time, s is balance time, t is chaos time, u is order time (All this R in seconds).<p>Note: Equality is needed for offline unlock." coords="69,557,125,612" shape="rect">
    <area target="" research="<p><img src=&quot;http://musicfamily.org/realm/Factions/picks/ArtoftheCrowTrophy.png&quot; align=&quot;middle&quot;><b> Art of the Crow Trophy</b></p> <p><b>Requirement</b>: Have any 6 complete Faction Artifact Sets.</p><p><b>Cost</b>: 1 Qavg (1.0e75)<p><b>Effect</b>: Gives upgrade with the same name.</p><p><b> Art of the Crow Upgrade</b></p> <p><b>Requirement</b>: Faction and Set Alignments has to match to buy the upgrade (Evil, Good, Neutral).</p><p>Order Effect: Multiplicatively increase max mana.</p><p>Chaos Effect: Multiplicatively increase assistants.</p><p>Balance Effect: Multiplicatively increase mana regeneration.</p><p><b>Good Effect</b>: The amount increased is based on on Excavations made.</p> <p><b>Formula</b>: (0.05 *  x ^ 1.1), where x is excavation count.</p><p><b>Evil Effect</b>: The amount increased is based on time spent in this game.</p> <p><b>Formula</b>: (4 * x ^ 0.44), where x is time spent this game.</p><p><b>Neutral Effect</b>: The amount increased is based on Royal Exchanges made</p> <p><b>Formula</b>: (0.8 * x ^ 0.8), where x royal exchanges made.</p>" coords="133,558,190,614" shape="rect">
